OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The son of a pensioner who died from   
OL,6, scalding injuries in a hotel bath has  
OL,7, described the frantic 90-minute attempt
OL,8, to rescue him as a "horror story".     
OL,10,FWallace Hunter died at the Pitlochry   
OL,11,FHydro in 2019 after being trapped in   
OL,12,Fthe bath, while guests and emergency   
OL,13,Fservices tried to smash in the door.   
OL,15,FEfforts to help the 75-year-old were   
OL,16,Fhampered by the door opening outwards  
OL,17,Fand being bolted from the inside.      
OL,19,FKeir Hunter has launched a civil action
OL,20,Fahead of a fatal accident inquiry.     
